file: EventStoreInterface.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\EventStoreInterface"
type: interface
summary: Defines the contract for persisting and retrieving execution events within the Agent Core system. It abstracts the underlying storage mechanism to ensure consistent interaction with run-specific event data. This interface serves as the primary boundary for event persistence operations.
